entry.title: fstxz/scene_tools
entry.summary: An editor plugin for Godot 4.2+ to help you with designing your levels and quick prototyping. It currently only supports asset placement.

entry.title: sscovil/godot-input-controller-addon
entry.summary: InputController plugin for the Godot game engine. Easily differentiate between a button tap, double tap, press, long press, and hold for all of your input actions in Godot.
